{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to Ploko, a VR adventure full of creativity and surprises!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udf0d BUILD MINIATURE WORLDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into a universe where <i>you\u2019re the creator</i>. Enjoy piecing together enchanting dioramas that come to life in themed landscapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488250/extras/BuildDioramas.gif?t=1739214878\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udcf7 CAPTURE MOMENTS AND UNCOVER SECRETS!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With the Polaroid camera, aim, snap\u2026 and sometimes, Ploko himself has hidden surprises waiting in your photos! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488250/extras/FindSecrets.gif?t=1739214878\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udf1f FOLLOW CLUES TO UNVEIL STORIES\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each diorama hides a mysterious story only you can reveal. Solve the photo challenges to learn more about Ploko\u2019s secret life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udfde\ufe0f EXPLORE A VARIETY OF ATHMOSPHERES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From serene Japanese gardens to bustling city streets, each level has its own unique style and charm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udc3e A FELINE COMPANION\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ploko, your friendly sidekick, accompanies you on your adventure, adding warmth and mystery to your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83c\udf08 EXPRESS YOUR CREATIVITY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Balancing relaxation and wonder, Ploko immerses you in a unique VR experience where each diorama invites you to dream.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic